Description:
    Generate internal Twirp API handlers and integration tests
    from a monolith-twirp-* gem.

    See https://github.com/github/monolith-twirp for more information.

Example:
    bin/rails generate twirp --from-gem monolith-twirp-NAMESPACE-NAME [--client CLIENT_NAME]

    This will create:
    - Handler classes under:
      app/api/internal/twirp/NAMESPACE/NAME/
    - Integration tests under:
      test/integration/api/internal/twirp/NAMESPACE/NAME/
